try what?
[/quote]try to pk just watch out for the muli cambat areas and clans and your picture how did u make it like that where u dont have to use the scroll bar to move around and it only shows what u want to see.[/quote]

Press the Print Screen key then open up paint and hit Ctrl + V. Then drag the box just over the Runescape screen and delete the rest. Then upload and ta-da you’re done.
